Arena Announcer: It was deemed too cruel, too dangerous! As
a result, the tournament's continuation was in doubt!

Arena Announcer: However, in such a notorious battlefield!
Today, brave and beautiful warriors have arrived!

Arena Announcer: Now, it's time for the warriors to enter
the arena!

Arena Announcer: With a great swordsmanship honed through
countless quests! A secret from the Adventurer's Guild, it's
Adventurer Clea!

Arena Announcer: Both in intellect and combat, she is the
strongest! The magician from the Magic Academy, Relm, has
arrived!

Arena Announcer: Unknown background, unknown identity! The
guards are asked to turn a blind eye! It's the thief Nora!

Arena Announcer: Healing or destroying, she does as she
pleases! The troublemaker from the Terios Church! It's the
priestess Sophia!

Thief Nora: I-It's not like I'll really get caught,
right?!

Priestess Sophia: Oh my, I wonder if Eleo-chan will scold
me again?

Magician Relm: Hehe, it's not bad to gather attention like
this!

Arena Announcer: We have gathered fierce beasts from all
over the empire for you to battle! If you can defeat all
five of these fierce beasts, you will be awarded the Crown
of the Resilient King!

Arena Announcer: Now, for the first match... the appearance
of a truly rare three-headed wolf!

Arena Announcer: What a splendid battle! But the next one
shouldn't be easily defeated either!

Arena Announcer: And now, for the second match... the
appearance of the man-eating tiger that caused havoc in
Mucos!

Arena Announcer: The fierce beasts are starting to look
pitiful! As expected of the brave warriors belonging to the
Adventurer's Guild!

Arena Announcer: And now, for the third match... the
appearance of a fire-breathing monster bird captured at the
remnants of judgment!

Arena Announcer: They're strong, too strong! This party has
an amazingly high level of skill!

Arena Announcer: The fourth round, where victory is within
sight... the appearance of the gluttonous monster that
destroyed the mine!

Arena Announcer: Unbelievable! The beautiful women have
made it to the final battle!

Arena Announcer: Next up is... everyone, prepare for
evacuation! It's the appearance of a hideous and detestable
monster accompanied by goblins!

Arena Announcer: The appearance of the captured orc by the
Imperial Army! Beautiful warriors, I beg of you! Please
win!
Arena Announcer: Huh... Something seems strange?

You have defeated the ogre... We need a more suitable
opponent than orcs!

General Atu: I will be your opponent in the final match.
Does anyone have any complaints?

Arena Announcer: Now, the strongest fierce beast has
arrived! The greatest general in the history of the Empire,
the guardian deity of the Empire, our eldest brother!

Arena Announcer: No one can complain! The battle of the
strongest man in the Empire! No blinking allowed! Pay
attention!

General Atu: Don't worry, I won't play around. However...
I'll let out some power against the ogre, just to be clear.

Arena Announcer: I-I can't believe it... Am I being shown
an illusion by the goddess Delia...?

General Atu: Hahaha, you're quite strong! The winners are
all of you, now let's give a round of applause to the
victors!

Arena Announcer: I-It's a tremendous victory! I can't
believe it, they've defeated General Atu!

Arena Announcer: The winners are Clea and her group! Today,
we are grateful to the goddess Actina for being able to
witness this!

Arena Announcer: Ah, I still can't believe it! I have
goosebumps, it was the greatest battle, the greatest
victory!

Announcer: The match has taken a big turn! It's a powerful
blow that blows away the shield!
Announcer: Will the golden-haired Golde win again!?

Apprentice Swordsman Auto: Huff... If things continue like
this... I won't be any different from before.

Announcer: Auto's powerful blow! However, it was deflected
and caused a fall!
Announcer: Is this going to be the decisive moment!?

Apprentice Swordsman Auto (I'm a coward... I'm not a strong
person like my father or Mr. Gale)

Apprentice Swordsman Auto (But Clea-san defeated the
dragon... Even I, a coward like me, can fight and defeat
it...!)
Clea: Haa... haa... Hang in there...
Clea: Please stand up, do your best!
Clea: Hang in there! Do your best, you coward!

Announcer: They've stood up! It seems Golde was waiting for
this!

Announcer: They continue to stare each other down... and
then, they moved!

Announcer: The match has come to an end! The winner of the
Pizuma Arena Special Individual Tournament is--
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
